INSERT INTO spk_cformleads VALUES('14', 'Mahak awan,Mawan@twu.edu,(682) 552-5430,Hello, I vibrated the office today about my problem, and I came over to the office but it seems that everyone is out of the office. As I mentioned before , I decided a misdemeanor c theft under 50 and I can get a deffered des position but I would rather get it expunged or disarmed completely no matter what I have to do, meaning community service hours or anything. I have never received a citation of any sort before and I would really like to get this removed. The lady in the office said Brent Bowen will charge me 250$ and go in for me. I have not revived my court date yet but they said it was fine. Also there were people there while I got fined , that we\\\'re going to jail but I DID NOT there is no record of me going to jail so the office mistakingly put \\\"arrest :yes \\\" on my citation , but I was NOT. You can beat contacted me through email and I really look forwar to getting some help for my future. I can come in on Wednesday at the earliest. Thank you!', '2013-11-11 19:11:59');
