INSERT INTO spk_cformleads VALUES('21', 'candace cabe,candacecabe@gmail.com,(214) 872-0222,My husband Joseph Hoffpauir was originally arrested on June 9, 2013 for bwi. They took him in for being the owner of our boat, even though we were not in motion and he was not driving the boat, I was. I bonded him out on 6/10/2013 and earlier this month probation informed him the interlock device was added to his bond conditions. His truck is in my name and they said he cannot have it installed in a vehicle that is not registered to him, that he needed to wait for his first court date and have the Judge sign for ankle monitor. Yesterday was his first court date and he was arrested on the spot without seeing the Judge. He is currently set for no bond and the bond company said an attorney can have his bond reinstated. The bond company has not dropped his bond, the court has. We need this done before the weekend because he is missing work and cannot afford to miss anymore.', '2013-11-22 03:07:29');
