INSERT INTO spk_cformleads VALUES('40', 'Leighton,leighton@hellofrisco.com,(972) 632-8091,Long story, ex has me in family court (judge Bailey every year)  The case is all post divorce and about modifications.  I\\\'ve spent over 50k past seven years including a trial which I was awarded everything I asked for.  I can no longer afford the standard 2-350 per hour rate.  I have a hearing scheduled for Jan. 22, for enforcement on 3 items, none have merit, in my opinion.  I\\\'ve been Pro Se for past seven months and since they are asking for Jail time I think I better attempt to have representation.  I can afford $125 per hour and do all of the work except representing myself in the hearing.  Are you interested in speaking.  I saw that you had one year experience, and is what I\\\'m looking for in order to find an affordable attorney.  If you can\\\'t do this rate thanks for your consideration and time.  I don\\\'t care if you have zero experience in family law as long as you can make legal objections and know the proper way to get evidence entered.  My ex-wife\\\'s lawyer is having a blast with me being Pro Se.  Hope you can help.\r\n\r\nLeighton Thetford', '2013-12-28 17:19:41');
