INSERT INTO spk_cformleads VALUES('44', 'Tonya Durham,tonya.r.durham@gmail.com,(214) 883-7477,My name is Tonya Durham and Corey Durham is my brother. Today he went to court for a DWI and was advised that he did not qualify for a Court Attorney. \r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nCorey was on probation already for a DWI that he got on New Years Eve in 2012 I think. October 2013 he got another one while texting as well. He went to court today and was advised that if he does not get an attorney he will go to jail. \r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nMy brother makes $12/hour and works part time as well as a waiter at Buffalo Wild Wings. I know he was stupid and got himself in this situation. But, he will not be able to pay bills or anything if he is in jail. I know you have heard this story a million times and you hear it everyday. I\\\'m not sure what else to do and your information was the first that popped up when I reviewed the website of Denton County Bar. \r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nPlease if there is any assistance, or help I\\\'m more than willing to accept or even take some advise. I do not want him to be in jail for a long period of time and I understand that, we may have to face jail time if we can not afford an attorney. We are not rich and we are barely what you would consider the working, poor middle class. \r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nAny advise would be appreciated to the 10th power. My name again is Tonya Durham and I can be reached at 214.883.7477. I hope to hear from you soon. He was advised that he has until Feb 4th. I\\\'m not sure what that means.', '2014-01-10 16:35:17');
INSERT INTO spk_cformleads VALUES('45', 'curtis ,crtskm@gmail.com,(469) 877-0706,My brother has failed dt or ua three times and he got arrested yesterday at probation office. I think third time is longer sentence not a week. We have received a court date a few days ago for purpose of motion to revoke on Feb can\\\'t remember the date. Do we need to.bail him out for the court date or will he face the judge while he\\\'s in jail? ', '2014-01-10 17:36:23');
INSERT INTO spk_cformleads VALUES('46', 'David Cooksey,davidcooksey34@gmail.com,(940) 205-7682,Hello my name is David Cooksey, and my wife is a Staff Sergeant in the U.S. Army. My wife and I were stationed in Katterbach Germany, and a couple of months ago I caught her in an affair. She moved me out of Germany, back here to the states where I am currently living with family. I have been back in the states for a little over a month, and during this time she has sent me separation paperwork. I have taken the paperwork to the legal office on Carswell Joint Reserve Base, and they have advised me to seek a civil legal attorney. We have a daughter, who is still living with my wife in Germany. I am afraid that my wife will try to keep me from seeing my daughter, and completely remove me from her life. The problem that I have is that I have no means of support at this time. I am currently attending college, and do not have employment. The Legal office on Carswell told me to look for a law firm that can do pro bono work or offer free consultation. Thank you for your time. ', '2014-01-10 21:11:58');
INSERT INTO spk_cformleads VALUES('47', 'Alisha Rawat,seoservicessince@yahoo.com,(000) 000-0000,Hi,\r\n\r\nHope you are well.\r\n\r\n1st Page on Google with Guaranteed!!\r\n\r\nLet me know if you would be interested in this.  We can schedule a call we will be pleased to explain our service in detail.\r\nNotes-: Kindly let me know your phone number and best timing along with time zone to give you a call to discuss more.\r\nI look forward to hearing from you.\r\n\r\nKind regards!\r\nAlisha Rawat', '2014-01-13 10:55:58');
