INSERT INTO spk_options VALUES('554', 'Law Firm (Levinson)_options', 'a:62:{s:10:\"style_head\";s:104:\"<link href=\'http://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Droid+Sans:400,700\' rel=\'stylesheet\' type=\'text/css\'>\";s:11:\"script_head\";s:0:\"\";s:14:\"code_afterbody\";s:0:\"\";s:16:\"check_smartsheet\";s:1:\"1\";s:11:\"lawyer_name\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"alert_emails\";s:24:\"seolawyers2012@gmail.com\";s:18:\"book_email_subject\";s:0:\"\";s:18:\"call_email_subject\";s:0:\"\";s:15:\"book_email_temp\";s:300:\"<h2>Attorney  [lawyername]  </h2>\r\n\r\nSomeone just downloaded your e-book from <br />your website and provided the following info: <br/>\r\n\r\n<br/>Name: [name] <br/>\r\nEmail: [email]<br/>\r\nPhone: [phone]<br/>\r\n\r\nThey are now a lead and should be contacted <br />immediately to see if they need help.<br/>\";s:16:\"phone_email_temp\";s:895:\"Attorney [lawyername],<br /><br />\r\n\r\nSomeone just dialed the tracking phone# on your<br />\r\nwebsite, and the call was forwarded to your office#.<br /><br />\r\n\r\nHere\'s the # that called you: [caller-id]<br /><br />\r\n    \r\nYou\'re getting this email with the caller ID shown<br />\r\nso you will know it came from someone who visited your<br />\r\nwebsite, and didn\'t just find you \'on the internet\'.<br /><br />\r\n\r\nCategorize the call, so at month\'s end, you\'ll have a<br />\r\nquick list that shows you what came in; for example:<br /><br />\r\n\r\nNew Potential Client<br />\r\nCurrent Client<br />\r\nPast Client<br />\r\nSolicitor<br />\r\nNon-Client Call<br />\r\n(judge, prosecutor, police, family)<br /><br />\r\n\r\nNot all calls are new potential clients, but I hope this<br />\r\none was and if so, that you retain them.<br /><br />\r\n\r\nRichard Jacobs<br />\r\nSpeakeasy Marketing, Inc.<br />\r\n585-309-0353 ph<br />\";s:11:\"home_slider\";s:17:\"[rev_slider home]\";s:16:\"home_testimonial\";s:198:\"Bill and Staff I want to thank you for representing me and achieving the result you did.  I am part