INSERT INTO spk_posts VALUES('29', '1', '2013-08-19 09:28:52', '2013-08-19 09:28:52', '<h1>High Caliber Denton Legal Representation:\r\nThe Bowen Law Group</h1>\r\nHandling complex legal issues can be extremely overwhelming, confusing, and stressful. It is vital to have an experienced advocate that can give advice and fight on your behalf, to keep your rights protected. When you need an attorney in Denton, Texas that you can trust, The Bowen Law Group certainly has the level of expertise that you will need. Each Denton attorney in our office concentrates in particular types of cases in many specific areas of law. Whether you need a Denton DWI attorney, a reputable Denton County divorce lawyer, a Denton criminal attorney, or a Frisco family lawyer for any other type of legal need in all areas of criminal and family law, you can count on professionalism, integrity, diligence, and experience with The Bowen Law Group. There is no need to take a chance by representing yourself pro se, when our lawyers are knowledgeable, skilled, and are more than willing to help you with everything from complex criminal defenses to family law issues.\r\n\r\n<h2>Why Choose The Bowen Law Group?</h2>\r\n\r\nWe practice in Denton, Collin, Wise and Cooke Counties. Whether you need a Lewisville divorce lawyer, or a seasoned Denton family law attorney to help with your case, we can put our expertise to work on your behalf. Our office proudly serves clients in Denton County, Flower Mound, Lewisville, Frisco, and the surrounding areas. Our attorneys understand that time is of the essence where your issues are concerned, and we will do everything within our power to get the results that you want professionally, effectively, and efficiently. Our attorneys are personable, and they are totally committed to the needs of our valued clients. Our Denton divorce attorney professionals and our Denton criminal lawyers are highly respected in the local communities that we serve, for our diligence and the comprehensive approaches that we take, to ensure that our clients get the best legal representation possible.\r\n<h2>Case Types That We Handle</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>DWI Cases and Drug Crimes</li>\r\n	<li>Assault, Burglary, Theft, and Robbery Cases</li>\r\n	<li>Non-Disclosure and Expunction</li>\r\n	<li>Probation Violations</li>\r\n	<li>Juvenile Law</li>\r\n	<li>Divorce, Child Custody, Child Support, Enforcement, and Modifications</li>\r\n	<li>All Other Types of Family Law and Criminal Law Cases</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>Contact Us Today!</h2>\r\nFor a criminal or divorce lawyer in Denton or the surrounding areas that you can count on, contact us today at [number type=\"1\"]. We will be more than happy to answer your inquiries, or to schedule an appointment so that you can consult with our lawyers about your case.', 'Home', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'home', '', '', '2013-10-25 13:07:28', '2013-10-25 13:07:28', '', '0', 'http://localhost/odelugojohnsonlaw/?page_id=29', '0', 'page', '', '0');
