hensive approaches that we take, to ensure that our clients get the best legal representation possible.\n\n<h2>Case Types That We Handle</h2>\n<ul>\n    <li>DWI Cases and Drug Crimes\n    <li>Assault, Burglary, Theft, and Robbery Cases\n    <li>Non-Disclosure and Expunction\n    <li>Probation Violations\n    <li>Juvenile Law\n    <li>Divorce, Child Custody, Child Support, Enforcement, and Modifications\n    <li>All Other Types of Family Law and Criminal Law Cases\n</ul>\n<h2>Contact Us Today!</h2>\n\nFor a criminal or divorce lawyer in Denton or the surrounding areas that you can count on, contact us today at [number type=\"1\"]. We will be more than happy to answer your inquiries, or to schedule an appointment so that you can consult with our lawyers about your case.', 'Home', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '29-autosave-v1', '', '', '2013-10-23 07:07:21', '2013-10-23 07:07:21', '', '29', 'http://localhost/odelugojohnsonlaw/?p=46', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
INSERT INTO spk_posts VALUES('47', '1', '2013-08-26 06:32:11', '2013-08-26 06:32:11', '<h1>South Carolina courts don\'t go easy on people arrested for drunk driving</h1>\r\nDrinking and driving don\'t mix, and South Carolina courts don\'t go easy on people arrested for drunk driving. Defending DUI can be as expensive as a conviction, but conviction impacts your life a lot harder.\r\n<h2>Trying to fight a DUI charge</h2>\r\nTrying to fight a DUI charge without professional legal representation can be disastrous, even for first-time offenders. If you or a loved one has been arrested for drunk driving (DUI) in South Carolina, it is critical to consult with an experienced DUI defense lawyer as soon as possible.\r\n<h3>Trying to fight a DUI charge</h3>\r\nAt Blake Law Firm, PA, our Florence DUI attorney works hard to help you get your life back on track in a way that satisfies the court but reduces your legal consequences as much as possible. Contact us today to schedule a consultation.\r\n<h4>Trying to fight a DUI charge</h4>\r\nBennettsville Drunk Driving Defense Attorney Advising on DUI Penalties and Consequences\r\n\r\nMost people don\'t consider the long-term consequences of a DUI conviction. Drunk or drugged driving often leads to reckless and inattentive driving, which can lead to accidental injury or even death. It is foolish to begin with, and it endangers everyone on the road, including the drunk driver and his or her passengers.\r\n\r\nA first DUI conviction includes:\r\nA stiff fine or up to one month in jail\r\nLoss of your driver\'s license\r\nHigher auto insurance premiums and potential consequences with your employer, depending on Â Â  Â Â Â  Â Â Â  Â your occupation\r\n\r\nThe legal blood alcohol concentration (BAC) limit in South Carolina is .08 percent. However, if your BAC was .10 percent or higher or you have been convicted of DUI before, the penalties you face increase.\r\n\r\nProfessional, Experienced Defense Across the Pee Dee Region\r\n\r\nOur law firm focuses on defending clients who have been charged with DUI in Bennettsville, Florence and surrounding areas. With more than 15 years of criminal defense experience, attorney Daniel Blake has a history of dedicated representation and advocacy in criminal and DUI matters. Our law firm is service-oriented and prepared to help you through this troubling legal matter.\r\n\r\nFree Initial Consultation With Attorney Daniel Blake\r\n\r\nIn your free initial consultation, Mr. Blake thoroughly answers all of your questions. He will also ask you a number of questions so that he can fully analyze your case. Although you face tough consequences, we can provide you with options to help you avoid or reduce the impacts a DUI conviction could have on your life.\r\nYou deserve straightforward legal advice and practical resolution to your case. Legal jargon doesn\'t protect your rights. The collaborative work of our office and an expert DUI investigator provides legal representation you can rely on.\r\nCost-Effective Services and Payment Plans to Fit Your Needs\r\nWe charge one flat legal fee regardless of how complicated your case is or the time it takes to obtain the best possible resolution. No one should face a drunk or drugged driving charge without experienced representation. We offer affordable payment plans to make the legal process easier.', 'Home', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '29-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-08-26 06:32:11', '2013-08-26 06:32:11', '', '29', 'http://localhost/odelugojohnsonlaw/?p=47', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
