s and litigators have an established reputation for dedication to their clients and aggressive legal counsel. If you have been injured by a defective product in Dallas, Arlington, Plano, or anywhere in Texas, contact us today to find out if you have a viable defective product claim and to get started on the path towards getting appropriate compensation. Call our Dallas office at 214-504-2121 or call toll free at 855-584-8787.', 'Home', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '29-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-09-12 08:58:46', '2013-09-12 08:58:46', '', '29', 'http://localhost/odelugojohnsonlaw/29-revision-v1/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
